<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l4">vnd <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> als Jr ſchreıbt / vvie vns <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l5"><expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / für ewch <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / etc . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir ſeinen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l6"><expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auf die cʒeit als er vns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> verſchraıb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l7"><expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / daʒ wir den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> deſmals <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> klag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l8">geweiſt <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Alſo daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> dem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l9"><expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒeit vnd <expan>Pfingſt<ex>en</ex></expan> tag beſchiede vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l11">des <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_500_line_1576352145974_5157">hülff </ab></add> / . vnd ſprıcht <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> vnſer / daʒ Jm das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒoge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l12"><expan>vvord<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeÿ / . Doch ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan> den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l13"><expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd ſein hawſfrawn daran geweıſt / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l14">ſie das beſteen <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllen <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>nehſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l15">ſant Mıchels tag / Alſo daʒ Jr mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
